{% comment %}
  FAQ Page - La Hime
  Converted from InfoPage.tsx type="faq"
{% endcomment %}

<div class="pt-44 pb-24 min-h-screen bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-16 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-pink max-w-none">
      <div class="space-y-12 text-gray-700">
        
        <section>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-6 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">Orders & Shipping</h3>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">Can I change or cancel my order?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We work fast! Once an order is placed, we have a very short window (about 1 hour) to make changes. Please email <span class="font-medium text-black">contact@lahime.com</span> immediately with your request.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">Where is my order confirmation?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Check your spam folder! If you still can't find it, ensure you entered the correct email address at checkout or contact support.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">Do you ship internationally?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, we ship globally! Please note that for orders outside the EU, custom duties and taxes may apply upon arrival and are the responsibility of the recipient.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-6 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">Product & Care</h3>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">How do I wash my La Hime items?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Most of our items feature delicate details like lace, satin, and rhinestones. We highly recommend <span class="font-bold">hand washing in cold water</span> or dry cleaning. Do not tumble dry.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">Are the size charts accurate?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, our sizing is based on standard European measurements. We have updated our size guide to CM to help you find the perfect fit. If you're between sizes, we generally suggest sizing up.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">Do you offer gift wrapping?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">All La Hime orders arrive in our signature pink packaging, making them perfect for gifting. You can add a personalized note at checkout.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-6 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">Payments</h3>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">What payment methods do you accept?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We accept major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Amex), PayPal, Apple Pay, and Google Pay.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
